{
  "stem": "25912.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But that was the first change.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And of course, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were-- the smaller the ghetto got, the more crowded it became.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the atmosphere was changing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] They were already bringing in, I think, Jews from smaller surrounding areas.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So the people around me were becoming more and more alien, in a way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were more sort of Hasidic Jews, people who would dress differently, had much more Yiddish, which was a foreign language to me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't understand what they were talking about.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They looked different.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So for a child, it was a strange environment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also, we were now-- the place where we were living faced a wall.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that meant that at night, which was a time when food was being smuggled into the ghetto, there were small children bringing in bread at night, making holes in the wall and bringing in sacks of potatoes, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Germans were shooting at night, so the nights were very disturbed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You could see, suddenly, flood lights and shooting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "On one occasion, the Germans came to the house, and in one of the apartments lived a journalist.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think his name was Warszawski.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was an old friend of my uncle, who was also a journalist.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they took him and his father out and shot them in the doorway.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't see it, but I heard it in the morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I heard the Germans coming in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I knew that in the morning, there was talk that they had been shot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there was-- every time somebody started banging on the gate, everybody was scared, because we just didn't know what was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there was this constant uncertainty.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
